<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Donation Receipt</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            padding: 24px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #111827;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #374151;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #111827;
        }
        .receipt {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 16px;
            background: #f3f4f6;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .receipt p {
            margin: 6px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: center;
        }
        a {
            color: #2563eb;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <h1>Thank you for your donation, {{donorName}}!</h1>
    <p>
        Weâ€™re grateful for your support. Below is a summary of your recent token donation:
    </p>

    <div class="receipt">
        <p><span class="highlight">Date:</span> {{date}}</p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Amount:</span> {{amount}} {{token}}</p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Transaction Hash:</span>
            <a href="{{explorerUrl}}" target="_blank">{{txHash}}</a>
        </p>
        <p><span class="highlight">Recipient:</span> {{recipient}}</p>
    </div>

    <p>
        Your contribution helps us continue our mission. This email serves as your donation receipt.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@beefunded.org">support@beefunded.org</a>.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} BeeFunded. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
